OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FA plasterer has been jailed after
OL,7,Fadmitting writing Facebook posts
OL,8,Finciting racial hatred.
OL,10,FDaniel Aaron Kingsley, from
OL,11,FFlintshire, appeared at Mold Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Thursday, 15 August, where he
OL,13,Fwas sentenced to 21 months in prison
OL,14,Fafter pleading guilty to distributing
OL,15,Fwritten material to stir up racial
OL,16,Fhatred ` an offence under Sections
OL,17,F19(1) and 27(3) of the Public Order
OL,18,FAct 1986.
