OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FDad-of-eight Kingsley, 33, of Plough
OL,7,FLane, Aston, was subsequently
OL,8,Fidentified as the account user and
OL,9,Farrested that day, and was later
OL,10,Fcharged.
OL,12,FKingsley was said to have shared his
OL,13,Ftwo posts on his private Facebook page
OL,14,F- which the court heard has 300
OL,15,Ffollowers - and on one platform. He
OL,16,Ftook them down himself and apologised,
OL,17,Fthe court heard.
