OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FProsecutor David Mainstone told the
OL,7,Fcourt the offence took place days
OL,8,Fafter widespread trouble across the UK
OL,9,Fand Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThere were disturbances including in
OL,12,FSouthport on July 30, Hartlepool on
OL,13,FJuly 31, Sunderland and Liverpool on
OL,14,FAugust 2, Belfast, Nottingham and Hull
OL,15,Fon August 3, Middlesbrough on August
OL,16,F4, and Birmingham, Plymouth and
OL,17,FBelfast on August 5, he said.
