OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FMr Mainstone said the defendant had
OL,7,F"clearly been aware" that these
OL,8,Fincidents were taking place. But he
OL,9,Ftold the court: "Nevertheless on
OL,10,FAugust 8 he posted on Facebook: "If
OL,11,Fyou believe these riots ain't right
OL,12,Fyou should not be in the UK and you
OL,13,Fshould not be allowed to be citizens
OL,14,Fof the UK."
OL,16,FMr Mainstone said Kingsley also made
OL,17,Fracial slurs against ethnic groups and
OL,18,Fsaid this country was "going down the
OL,19,Fsh***er". He added in the post: "We
OL,20,Fhave had beheadings, now stabbings of
OL,21,Fkids - when will they learn?"
