OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FIn a second post on August 10,
OL,7,FKingsley wrote on Facebook: "If you
OL,8,Fare going to riot today do it
OL,9,Fproperly." He referred to a number of
OL,10,Fareas, including a property where
OL,11,Fmigrants were housed where police had
OL,12,Falready stepped up patrols.
OL,14,FHe told officers he had copied and
OL,15,Fpasted the first post and the words
OL,16,Fhad not been his own. He now knows the
OL,17,Fwords were disgusting and accepted
OL,18,Fthey could be deemed racist.
