OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FThe second post was put up because he
OL,7,Fdid not want a riot near his home and
OL,8,Ffamily. But his father and wife saw
OL,9,Fthe posts and he took the posts down.
OL,11,FHe prosecutor said Kingsley denied
OL,12,Fbeing racist, although the judge
OL,13,Fremarked: "They always do."
OL,15,FAlexandra Carrier, defending, said the
OL,16,Fposts were to friends not the public
OL,17,Fand he removed them himself. She said
OL,18,Fher client had never engaged in
OL,19,Fracially aggravated offending before
OL,20,Fand was sorry.
