OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FHe had stopped offending more
OL,7,Fgenerally after meeting his wife who
OL,8,Fput him on the right track, the court
OL,9,Fheard. He has eight children,
OL,10,Fincluding a severely autistic son and
OL,11,Fcares for his stepfather and mother.
OL,13,FOn his offending, she said: "He is
OL,14,Fdevastated he did it. He knows he has
OL,15,Ffailed his wife and children."
OL,17,FThe court also heard that Kingsley,
OL,18,Fwho appeared on video link from HMP
OL,19,FBerwyn, had a hernia operation on
OL,20,FSunday and is in some pain.
