OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FThe judge, His Honour Rhys Rowlands,
OL,7,Fcondemned Kingsley's behaviour calling
OL,8,Fhim a bigot.
OL,10,FHe said: "On 9 July three innocent
OL,11,Fyoung children were killed in
OL,12,FSouthport in an act which both shocked
OL,13,Fand united right-thinking people who
OL,14,F(felt) revulsion and horror at what
OL,15,Ftook place, and sympathy for the
OL,16,Ffamilies and friends of those tragic
OL,17,Fvictims.
OL,19,F"Within hours others were seeking to
OL,20,Ftake advantage of the situation,
OL,21,Fspreading lies and misinformation."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
