OL,6,FThis would have been frightening for
OL,7,Fmembers of ethnic minorities and
OL,8,Fpolice officers called out to protect
OL,9,Fcommunities, added the judge.
OL,11,FHe added "thankfully the mindless and
OL,12,Fdisgraceful thuggery was not
OL,13,Freplicated here in Wales", although
OL,14,Fbigots like the defendant played their
OL,15,Fpart by writing "deeply offensive
OL,16,Fracist posts".
OL,18,FJudge Rowlands said: "Your intention
OL,19,Fwas to incite or encourage serious
OL,20,Fviolence...
