OL,3,CPlasterer jailed over two Facebook
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,F"Those who propagate hate and racial
OL,7,Fdivision must accept the consequences."
OL,9,FChief Constable Amanda Blakeman KPM
OL,10,Fsaid: "North Wales Police takes any
OL,11,Fallegation of criminality, whether
OL,12,Fcommitted online or in person,
OL,13,Fextremely seriously.
OL,15,F"This type of offending causes fear
OL,16,Fwithin communities and as this case
OL,17,Fdemonstrates, those who engage in
OL,18,Fonline offending in such a way will be
OL,19,Fidentified and placed before the
OL,20,Fcourt."
